  "body": "### Component\n\nCast\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nI'd like to be able to send transactions, make `eth_call`s or do gas estimation with calldata directly instead of passing in a function selector + args. This is useful when handling data that has already been ABI encoded or if the calldata is not following ABI.\r\n\r\n`seth` does have this feature, it would require some refactoring to allow `cast` to do so but it should definitely be possible.\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
